\c 53
\s Vanhu vese vakashata
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; pamuimbirwo weMaharati. Rwiyo rweMashiri rwaDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Benzi rakati mumoyo maro, Mwari hakuna . Vakaora, vakaita zvakaipa zvinonyangadza; Hakuna anoita zvakanaka.
\v 2 Mwari, ari kudenga, wakatarira pasi kuvana vavanhu, Kuti aone kana akachenjera aripo, Anotsvaka Mwari.
\v 3 Umwe neumwe wavo akadzokera shure; vakasvibiswa pamwechete; Hakuna anoita zvakanaka, kunyange nomumwe.
\v 4 Ko vaiti vezvakaipa havana zivo here? Ivo vanodya vanhu vangu sechingwa, Vasingadani kuna Mwari.
\v 5 Vaitya kwazvo ipapo, pakange pasina chinotyisa; nokuti Mwari akaparadza mafupa aiye akange akakukomba; Iwe wakavanyadzisa, nokuti Mwari akavarasi a.
\v 6 Dai kuponeswa kwaIsraeri kwaibva paZiyoni! Kana Mwari achidzosa vanhu vake pakutapwa, Ipapo Jakove achafara kwazvo naIsraeri achafara.
